 call them, The border of wickedness, and, The people against whom the LORD hath indignation for ever.","year":-397},{"id":"reczOYkVTRiAIogae","ref":"Mal.1.5","text":"And your eyes shall see, and ye shall say, The LORD will be magnified from the border of Israel.","year":-397},{"id":"recovVmGtImjolqzG","ref":"Mal.1.6","text":"A son honoureth his father, and a servant his master: if then I be a father, where is mine honour? and if I be a master, where is my fear? saith the LORD of hosts unto you, O priests, that despise my name. And ye say, Wherein have we despised thy name?","year":-397}]}
